<br>
The other thing is Rage is an overgrown Naggy. Has a few more hp. Casts a 500pt AoE that is resistable but be over 150 or so instead of the 100 needed for Naggy. Also plan on fighting debuffed. Rage dispells 4 buffs at once just like Naggy but does it several times during the fight. First time I did it I had 15 buffs going in and one buff at the end. Put your Hit Point and fire resist buffs on last so you keep them longer but you will lose them unless you kill Rage really fast. Last couple times I did Rage we had all level 60's and less than 3 groups and no one died. Oh one other thing, Manaburn and Soloists Spear of ice usually do full damage so if you got any 60 wizzies the fight gets a lot easier. <p><img src="http://www.terstai.net/~terstai/images/Baledorsig2.jpg"><BR> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=402751" target="_blank">My Stuff</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ufaederya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Faederya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 155<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/16/02 9:17:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1375.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Ragefire:  Gonna burn few charges of Snare Gland</span><hr size=1> He fears also...<br>
